OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost of living: Gordon     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBrown urges action on      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fextreme poverty            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents are struggling to keep their   
OL,6, children warm at night due to the cost 
OL,7, of living crisis, says Gordon Brown.   
OL,9,FThe former Labour prime minister said  
OL,10,Fthere was a growing need for pillows,  
OL,11,Fduvets, sheets and even beds as people 
OL,12,Fwere left sleeping on the floor.       
OL,14,FMr Brown and Wales First Minister Mark 
OL,15,FDrakeford have written to Rishi Sunak  
OL,16,Fto ask for more help for the poorest.  
OL,18,FMr Sunak promised to "stand by" those  
OL,19,Fstruggling with the soaring cost of    
OL,20,Fessentials in his Spring Statement.    
